          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Puerto Rico Emergency Financial Stability Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill grants a temporary stay (until April 1, 2016, with specified exceptions) of any litigation, liens, or other collection actions to recover debts owed by the government of the Commonwealth of Puerto Rico and allows relief from such stay only in limited circumstances.</p>]]></text>
